node.text:
We kindly ask, what ISN'T better served on a bed of fries? Like, nothing. Please let's put everything on fries! Especially sweet potato fries. And these dreamies with their salty Mediterranean-inspired flavors from marinated chickpeas, tomatoes, feta cheese, creamy tzatziki sauce, and crunchy romaine. And did we slap some crispy homemade fried pita strips on top of that pile as well? We sure did.⠀
⠀
Get the recipe --> https://pinchofyum.com/street-cart-fries ⠀
⠀

node.text:
This little unicorn somehow manages to feel like a comfort food with its rich creamy sauce (thank you, coconut creeeaaam!) and tender chicken but still taste super bright, fresh, and summery, courtesy of the zippy lemongrass flavor and bunches of lime zest and fresh cilantro. It's all piled on top of some steamy rice with tender-crisp and golden brown little zucchinis (because hi, summer veg abundance). Yum yum yuuuum, we cannot stop with this.⠀

Yes YES, summer is for pasta! Especially this pasta. Wide, flat, beautiful pappardelle (oh thank you so, @delallofoods) twisting all around a bunch of summery produce like bursty cherry tomatoes, bright zucchini, and sweet crunchy fresh corn (but you can get creative with whatever garden goods you have.) A little luscious light cream sauce to hold it all together and then, AND THEN, the most perfect pan-fried chicken right alongside it all. Whoo, this one's a gem.⠀
